    public class InMemoryDOMDataStore
extends java.lang.Object
implements DOMStore, org.opendaylight.yangtools.concepts.Identifiable<java.lang.String>, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.model.api.SchemaContextListener, java.lang.AutoCloseable
    In-memory DOM Data Store Implementation of DOMStore which uses DataTree and other classes such as SnapshotBackedWriteTransaction. SnapshotBackedReadTransaction and ResolveDataChangeEventsTask to implement DOMStore contract.
